MIND MELTER

Mind Melters are the ultimate psychic beings, humans born with total
mastery of psionic ability across every known category.  They are more
powerful than any trained psychic OCC and serve as natural leaders, scouts,
and weapons in any group that can tolerate the stares that follow them into
every room.  The Coalition hunts Mind Melters on sight.

ATTRIBUTES (approximate ranges):
  IQ: 5-20   ME: 7-22   MA: 5-20   PS: 3-18
  PP: 3-18   PE: 3-18   PB: 3-18   Spd: 3-18

DAMAGE POOL:
  SDC: 1d4 x10 + PE (approx 10-40 + PE)

SPECIAL ABILITIES:
  - Master psionic: access to all four psionic categories
  - Telepathy: read surface thoughts
  - Telekinesis: move objects with the mind
  - Empathy: sense and project emotions
  - Mind Block auto-defence: automatically blocks hostile psionic attack
  - Enhanced IQ, ME, and MA attributes

PENALTIES:
  - Not OCC eligible, psionic mastery IS the path
  - Hunted by Coalition, Psi-Stalkers, and certain supernatural beings
  - Psychic burnout if ISP is depleted: penalties to all actions
  - Emotional instability under extreme stress

OCC ELIGIBLE: No.
ALIGNMENT: Any.

See also: burster, cs_psi-stalker, races
